.:: Einstein-puzzle ::.

There 5 different types of food: mango, pineapple, cherry, broccoli, garlic
There are 5 different nationalities: british, danish, german, norwegian, swede
There are 5 different favourite beverages: beer, coffee, milk, tea, water
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: bellflower, rose, orchid, zinnia, amaryllis
City: new-york, paris, boston, hamburg, hannover
1. the british is the person eating cherry
2. the swedish is the person traveling to boston
3. the danish is the person drinking tea
4. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person eating broccoli
5. the person eating pineapple is the person drinking coffee
6. the person who growsorchid is the person traveling to paris
7. the person eating garlic is the person who growsrose
8. the person drinking milk is in the middle
9. the norwegian is on the far left
10. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person traveling to new-york
11. the person traveling to hannovers is on the left or right of the person who growsrose
12. the person who growsbellflower is the person drinking beer
13. the german is the person who growszinnia
14. the norwegian is on the left or right of the person eating mango
15. the person who growsamaryllis is on the left or right of the person drinking water

.:: Answer ::.
|		|	1	|	2	|	3	|	4	|	5	|
| Food		|    garlic	|     mango	|      cherry	|     pineapple	|     broccoli	|
| Nationality	|   norwegian	|    danish	|    british	|    german	|    swedish	|
| City		|     new-york	|    hannover	|     paris	|     hamburg	|      boston	|
| Beverage	|    water	|     tea	|     milk	|    coffee	|      beer	|
| Flower		|   rose	|    amaryllis	|  orchid	|    zinnia	|   bellflower	|
